{"type":"message","id":"12812a00","parentId":"a92e634d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:23:42.991Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. The sessions listed are:\n1. The cron job session (agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978)\n\nThis is not a user conversation - it's just the cron job running. I should check if there's any other session with recent user activity. The session shown has \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\" and is the cron session itself. There are no actual user messages in the last 5 minutes.\n\nActually, let me reconsider - the sessions_list shows only the cron session itself. There are no other user sessions. So there are no active user conversations.\n\nWait, but the task says \"如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息）\". The sessions_list only shows the cron job session, which means there are no other user sessions active. So I should proceed with the autonomous learning.\n\nBut wait - this cron job session itself was triggered at 4:23 PM and is the current session. \n\nThe question is whether a cron job counts as an \"active user conversation\" - by definition it doesn't, since it's a scheduled task rather than a user-initiated interaction. So I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.","thinkingSignature":"98c9072c9bc3dc54978fcd7cddf9d0bcdc9f0d4092aa126e49a9508e617d166b"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有cron任务自身会话（agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978），没有用户发起的活跃对话。执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h4ovy7g2sc4p_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":663,"output":348,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44992,"cost":{"input":0.00019889999999999998,"output":0.00041759999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019359299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775031809412}}
{"type":"message","id":"38fba3f2","parentId":"12812a00","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:23:42.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_h4ovy7g2sc4p_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775031822994}}
{"type":"message","id":"61144e82","parentId":"38fba3f2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:23:50.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll perform web searches for the relevant industry topics. Let me search for:\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业趋势\n4. IT运维服务最新发展\n5. 弱电工程行业发展","thinkingSignature":"4b65f5074df59c3a18dc02284506f49d81e694a1f37b0f9514fa036c95b9e3e1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q0che52553kb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q0che52553kb_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q0che52553kb_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1526,"output":243,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45750,"cost":{"input":0.00045779999999999996,"output":0.0002916,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00206883}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775031822998}}
